high_descs: Turn to the right, and then the left to face the sink.
Pick up the soap from the far back right corner.
Place the soap in the sink and turn the water on. Turn it off and take the soap out.
Carry the soap and turn left to go to the bath tub.
Place the soap inside the bath tub, towards the middle.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bar of soap and move it to the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn right, head to toilet, turn left, go to sink on the right.
Pick up the soap next to the sink.
Wash the soap in the sink with water.
Bring the washed soap to the tub on the left.
Put the soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap in the tub.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen sink on the right.
Grab the pink bar of soap.
Place the soap inside the sink, then soak it.
Grab the wet bar of soap and walk to the bathtub.
Place the bar of soap inside the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Get a wet bar of soap inside the bathtub.
